# Bootstrap Instructions (ONE-TIME USE)

## CRITICAL: Read This First

**These are ONE-TIME bootstrap instructions. You are seeing this because no .cursor/rules/ directory exists yet.**

**Your task:**
1. **Ask the user clarifying questions** about project goals and scope (DO NOT ASSUME)
